'Merged PR 9575: [PUP][Sort] - Made quarriable ituff tokens case insensitive'
'Merged PR 10330: Enable Mega Template ScanLYATestMethod'
'Merged PR 10095: Merged PR 9030: adding strgval SetData API to be able to accept List of string'
'Merged PR 9556: [CherryPick] Merged PR 9530: [DatalogService] [CompositeFormat] Allow overwrite default data precision for CompositeFormat.'
'Merged PR 9502: [DataLog] Making possible to run SetData before SetCustomTname in StrgvalFormat'</releaseNotes>
